{"tid":502583,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［絲打入］評論我是否賤男","createTime":"2017-12-18T04:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T09:51:48.000Z","uid":153790,"like":2,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a69b6921d27d83b4eb7eae3d8410b1de80e45f2a","tid":502583,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T04:56:57.000Z","msg":"背景：同女朋友一齊2年幾，大家同齡人<br />\n<br />\n講左衰野先：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.女友為我食左2年事前避孕藥<br />\n原因係我條撚太大 <br />\n搵唔到合適+薄既套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次一戴套就搞到鳩縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為個套太細 <br />\n女友出盡全力咁塞入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塞到又痛又敏感<br />\n同埋我中意中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.成日做錯野激嬲佢 包括有<br />\n臨時甩底、無交帶、錯唔肯認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發皮氣訂爛佢既野 包括有<br />\n膠紙座、房門、一塊鏡、擺設等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3.成日同佢冷戰（1星期至1個月不等）<br />\n因為唔想認錯+氹佢<br />\n佢成日為個小小嬲我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我認為既小事就係第2點<br />\n<br />\n講番好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.我好錫佢 上年買左部i7比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整過1次布甸比佢+煲過1次野比佢飲<br />\n<br />\n2.我個處比左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3.幫佢供左1萬幾蚊脫毛費用<br />\n因為佢想脫腋下同個西<br />\n連陰唇佢都脫埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 光脫脫<br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4.暫時未出過軌，除左睇av同某些ig女神<br />\n<br />\n試問我在絲打心目中是否賤男<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef825a1e112700687d2c5a7cdae6c45b165c9198","tid":502583,"uid":132296,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T04:59:37.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"5a56429d6c1d49e4f6991a3396f663b51312768c","tid":502583,"uid":38668,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"唔想知 請返5p"},{"pid":"65a3eff1e1197f9422535f1d512a841ae3c43195","tid":502583,"uid":3908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:09:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15077fceb05ba3fb81edf58e34f799eb9dc659d2","tid":502583,"uid":108328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:17:13.000Z","msg":"影碌撚上黎睇下有幾大先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041fdd3741cf850d4d93380777f7f08515e85e68","tid":502583,"uid":103709,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:22:22.000Z","msg":"你係咪賤男就唔知<br />\n但就幾肯定你係一條on9"},{"pid":"e50f6b54da5534f62f24b913f8ab45f6f7b665d3","tid":502583,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪賤男就唔知<br />\n但就幾肯定你係一條on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd41d692c431fddf251d4eef24e5f4c327d4e40b","tid":502583,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"好想試下樓主條野"},{"pid":"ff6fc76711a6073993a67da3e1321c3d608ca7cc","tid":502583,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想試下樓主條野</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /